'''2011年錫金地震'''（{{lang-hi|'''२०११ सिक्किम ज़लज़ला'''|translit=Sikkim Zalzalā}}）或稱'''2011年喜馬拉雅地震'''，震央位於[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]及[[錫金邦|錫金邦]]交界的[[干城章嘉峰保護區|干城章嘉峰保護區]]內，地震規模為6.9，發生於當地時間2011年9月18日18時10分（[[UTC|UTC]]12時40分）<ref name=data>{{cite news |title=Magnitude 6.8 - SIKKIM, INDIA |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0005wg6.php |publisher=[[United_States_Geological_Survey|United States Geological Survey]] (USGS) |date=2011-09-18 |accessdate=2011-09-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921163147/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0005wg6.php |archivedate=2011-09-21 }}</ref>，於[[印度|印度]]北部、尼泊爾、[[不丹|不丹]]、[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]及[[中华人民共和国|中国]][[西藏|西藏]]南部皆可感受到震動。

此次地震共造成111人死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/sikkim-earthquake-gangtok-rescue-operations-death-toll/1/151950.html|title=Quake toll rises to 68 in India, relief team reaches epicentre in Sikkim|date=2011-09-20|accessdate=2011-09-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204145/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/sikkim-earthquake-gangtok-rescue-operations-death-toll/1/151950.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，多數分布於錫金邦<ref>[http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2465147.ece?homepage=true Earthquake claims two lives in Sikkim] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2465147.ece?homepage=true |date=20131111193402 }}, [[The_Hindu|The Hindu]], 2011-09-18</ref>，於[[甘托克|甘托克]]則有數棟建築倒塌<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/18/us-quake-india-idUSTRE78H19D20110918 |title=Magnitude 6.8 quake in India, several dead |publisher=Reuters |date= |accessdate=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155255/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/18/us-quake-india-idUSTRE78H19D20110918 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；於尼泊爾造成6人死亡，包括[[加德滿都|加德滿都]]的[[英國|英國]][[大使館|大使館]]圍牆倒塌造成3人死亡<ref>[http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report_earthquake-kills-5-in-nepal_1588802 Earthquake kills 5 in Nepal] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report_earthquake-kills-5-in-nepal_1588802 |date=20121005224112 }}, [[Daily_News_and_Analysis|DNA]], 2011-09-18</ref>，[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]][[西藏自治区|西藏自治区]]的[[亚东县|亚东县]]也传出有7人死亡。
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20110922/4652633.shtml|title=印度锡金邦6.8级地震造成西藏7人遇难136人伤|date=2011-09-22|accessdate=2011-09-23|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608020656/http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20110922/4652633.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
於錫金地震發生前幾天，印度[[哈里亚纳邦|哈里亚纳邦]]索尼伯德地區發生規模4.2的地震<ref name="Earthquake-report.com">{{cite web|title=Very strong earthquake in SIKKIM, India|url=http://earthquake-report.com/2011/09/18/very-strong-earthquake-in-sikkim-india/|work=2011-09-18|publisher=Earthquake-report.com|accessdate=2011-09-18|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620030204/https://earthquake-report.com/2011/09/18/very-strong-earthquake-in-sikkim-india/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而錫金地震為2011年印度的第4個及世界第15個大地震。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sikkim quake is India's fourth this september|url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/sikkim-quake-is-indias-fourth-this-september-134548?pfrom=home-bigstory|accessdate=2011-09-18|newspaper=[[NDTV|NDTV]]|date=2011-09-18|archive-date=2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009111455/http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/sikkim-quake-is-indias-fourth-this-september-134548?pfrom=home-bigstory|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="toll">{{cite news|title=Sikkim earthquake toll rises to 50|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-toll-rises-to-50/articleshow/10040635.cms|accessdate=2011-09-19|newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|date=2011-09-19|archive-date=2019-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622042859/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-toll-rises-to-50/articleshow/10040635.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==地質==
這起[[矩震級|矩震級]]6.9（Mw）的主震是發生於2011年9月18日當地時間18:10（12:40 UTC），震源大約在印度錫金邦甘多克西北方68公里處，深度19.7公里（12.2英里）的淺層地震<ref name=data /> 。於震央附近地區，地震約持續30至40秒<ref name="times">{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/eight-killed-100-injured-as-strong-quake-jolts-sikkim-nepal-border-region/articleshow/10031582.cms|title=Eight killed, 100 injured as strong quake jolts Sikkim-Nepal border region|date=2011-09-18|accessdate=2011-09-18|work=The Economic Times|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020044132/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/eight-killed-100-injured-as-strong-quake-jolts-sikkim-nepal-border-region/articleshow/10031582.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
===餘震===
於主震發生後30分鐘內，錫金地區分別發生三次規模各為5.7、5.1及4.6的餘震。<ref name=Aftershocks>{{cite news|title=2 killed in Sikkim, buildings hit as quake jolts Northeast|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_2-killed-in-sikkim-buildings-hit-as-quake-jolts-northeast_1588715|accessdate=2011-09-18|newspaper=[[Daily_News_and_Analysis{{!}}DNA_India|Daily News and Analysis{{!}}DNA India]]|date=2011-09-18|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005224129/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_2-killed-in-sikkim-buildings-hit-as-quake-jolts-northeast_1588715|dead-url=no}}</ref>加德滿都則發生兩次規模4.8的餘震，並無該地區嚴重災情<ref name="Earthquake in Nepal, September 18.">{{cite web|title=Earthquake in Nepal, September 18.|url=http://wearenepali.blogspot.com/2011/09/earthquake-in-nepal-september-18.html|accessdate=2011-09-18|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608142659/http://wearenepali.blogspot.com/2011/09/earthquake-in-nepal-september-18.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少20次以上的餘震也造成甘托克居民恐慌<ref name="toll"/>。於9月19日在[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]也發生規模3.9的地震<ref name="Quake rattles Maharashtra">{{cite news|title=Quake rattles Maharashtra|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/nation/west/quake-rattles-maharashtra-839|accessdate=2011-09-19|newspaper=[[The_Deccan_Chronicle|The Deccan Chronicle]]|date=2011-09-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919145903/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/nation/west/quake-rattles-maharashtra-839|archivedate=2011-09-19}}</ref>，約發生於當地時間6時30分，所影響的地區包括[[拉杜爾|拉杜爾]]、[[奧斯曼阿巴德|奧斯曼阿巴德]]及[[索拉普|索拉普]]地區皆曾於1993年遭遇[[1993年拉杜爾地震|拉杜爾地震]]影響<ref name="Earthquake jolts several parts of Maharashtra today">{{cite web |title=Earthquake jolts several parts of Maharashtra today |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Earthquake-jolts-several-parts-of-Maharashtra-today/articleshow/10036836.cms |work=2011-09-19 |publisher=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919092321/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Earthquake-jolts-several-parts-of-Maharashtra-today/articleshow/10036836.cms |archivedate=2011-09-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，不過19日的地震並無造成災害<ref>{{cite web|title=Quake jolts several parts of Maharashtra|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/quake-jolts-several-parts-of-maharashtra/185382-3.html|publisher=[[CNN-IBN|CNN-IBN]]|accessdate=2011-09-19|archive-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817205214/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/quake-jolts-several-parts-of-maharashtra/185382-3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

