地震造成建築物倒塌及[[土石流|土石流]]，部分地區通訊中斷、停電<ref name="times"/>。9月仍是[[南亞|南亞]]的雨季，大雨造及土石流造成救援更加困難<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/sikkim-the-morning-after-offers-a-grim-picture-134694 |title=Sikkim the morning after offers a grim picture |publisher=Ndtv.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202145422/http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/sikkim-the-morning-after-offers-a-grim-picture-134694 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===印度===
此次地震主要災情分布於印度北部<ref name="toll">{{cite news|title=Sikkim earthquake toll rises to 50|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-toll-rises-to-50/articleshow/10040635.cms|accessdate=2011-09-19|newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|date=2011-09-19}}</ref>，僅錫金邦就造成至少60人死亡<ref name="35 tourists airlifted, toll crosses 90">{{cite news|title=35 tourists airlifted, toll crosses 90|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-35-tourists-airlifted-toll-crosses-90/articleshow/10063310.cms|accessdate=2011-09-21|newspaper=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|date=2011-09-21|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002755/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-35-tourists-airlifted-toll-crosses-90/articleshow/10063310.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於[[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]至少7人死亡，於[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]也有6人死亡<ref name="Sikkim earthquake toll climbs to 66, rescue work hampered by landslides">{{cite web|title=Sikkim earthquake toll climbs to 66, rescue work hampered by landslides|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-toll-climbs-to-66-rescue-work-hampered-by-landslides/articleshow/10041847.cms|work=2011-09-19|publisher=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|accessdate=2011-09-19|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822095233/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Sikkim-earthquake-toll-climbs-to-66-rescue-work-hampered-by-landslides/articleshow/10041847.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===中國===
於[[西藏|西藏]][[亞東縣|亞東縣]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/detail_2011_09/19/9294991_0.shtml |title=印度锡金邦地震造成西藏7人死亡 亚东县受灾严重_资讯频道_凤凰网 |publisher=News.ifeng.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604102738/http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/detail_2011_09/19/9294991_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[定结县|定结县]]及[[岗巴县|岗巴县]]<ref name="ifeng1">{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/society/news/detail_2011_09/19/9280777_0.shtml |title=受印度地震影响西藏边境地区部分房屋倒塌 一人受伤_资讯频道_凤凰网 |publisher=News.ifeng.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609010159/http://news.ifeng.com/society/news/detail_2011_09/19/9280777_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>傳出房屋倒塌，亞東縣則有7人死亡<ref>{{cite web |author=3088 |url=http://119.people.com.cn/GB/15693712.html |title=西藏亚东县7人因地震死亡 消防救援-社会-人民网 |publisher=119.people.com.cn |date= |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archive-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402220534/http://119.people.com.cn/GB/15693712.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===尼泊爾===
於尼泊爾首都加德滿都造成的損害相對較小<ref name="Earthquake in Nepal, September 18."/>，但英國大使館的圍牆倒塌造成3人死亡；較靠近震央的尼泊爾東部災情較為嚴重，造成數百棟房屋毀損，先前的大雨使得飽水土壤發生土石流災害<ref>{{cite web|url=http://reliefweb.int/node/447465|title=Quake hits vast Himalayan region killing 63|date=2011-09-19|accessdate=2011-09-19|publisher=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]|first=Prakash|last=Adhikari}}</ref>。地震造成[[孫薩里|孫薩里]]地區通訊中斷、停電<ref name="Earthquake in Nepal, September 18."/>。於Dharan則有2人死亡<ref name="Powerful quake rocks Nepal, at least five killed">{{cite web|title=Powerful quake rocks Nepal, at least five killed|url=http://www.nepalmountainnews.com/cms/?p=38813|work=2011-09-18|publisher=Nepalmountainnews.com|accessdate=2011-09-18|archive-date=2013-01-04|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130104023455/http://www.nepalmountainnews.com/cms/?p=38813|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
===孟加拉===
於孟加拉北部震感較強烈，在[[達卡|達卡]]、[[錫爾赫特|錫爾赫特]]、[[福里德布爾|福里德布爾]]、[[博格拉|博格拉]]皆能感受震動<ref name=bd>{{cite news|title=6.8 tremor jolts Dhaka, Ctg, Sylhet|url=http://bdnews24.com/details.php?id=206403&cid=2|accessdate=2011-09-18|newspaper=bdnews24.com|date=2011-09-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925090250/http://bdnews24.com/details.php?id=206403&cid=2|archivedate=2011-09-25}}</ref>。有少量建築物磁磚剝落<ref name=bd2>{{cite news|title=Two Dhaka buildings damaged in quake|url=http://bdnews24.com/details.php?cid=2&id=206404&hb=2|accessdate=2011-09-18|newspaper=bdnews24.com|date=2011-09-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402071635/http://bdnews24.com/details.php?cid=2&id=206404&hb=2|archivedate=2012-04-02}}</ref>，並未傳出傷亡<ref name=bd-toi>{{cite news|title=Powerful quake jolts Bangladesh, sparks panic|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Powerful-quake-jolts-Bangladesh-sparks-panic/articleshow/10032567.cms|accessdate=2011-09-18|newspaper=Times of India|date=2011-09-18|archive-date=2019-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702140425/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Powerful-quake-jolts-Bangladesh-sparks-panic/articleshow/10032567.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

